description:
This is a 16 minute workout called 'Yoga For Depression - Yoga With Adriene' from the channel Yoga With Adriene.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Yoga For Depression is a 15 min yoga practice to help balance and restore both the physical and emotional body. Tend to your nervous system through mindful yoga to tend to the brain and body connect in a powerful way. With a focus on the breath, this yoga practice invites you to be kind, be accepting, practice regularly, and heal naturally.
